### ========================================
### Example 1: Basic GET - All articles without any filters
### ========================================

GET http://localhost:8080/api/articles
Accept: application/json

### ========================================
### Example 2: Get articles WITH PRICES for a specific date
### ========================================

GET http://localhost:8080/api/articles?date=2026-02-04&withPrices=true
Accept: application/json

### ========================================
### Example 3: Get only articles WITH ACTIVE DISCOUNTS
### ========================================

GET http://localhost:8080/api/articles?date=2026-02-04&discountOnly=true
Accept: application/json

### ========================================
### Example 4: Get articles with prices AND filter by discount
### ========================================

GET http://localhost:8080/api/articles?date=2026-02-04&withPrices=true&discountOnly=true
Accept: application/json

### ========================================
### Example 5: Different date - Spring promotion active
### ========================================

GET http://localhost:8080/api/articles?date=2026-03-15&withPrices=true
Accept: application/json

###
GET http://localhost:8080/api/articles?date=2026-03-15&discountOnly=true
Accept: application/json

